## Spacing Scale

```
4   8   10  12  16  20  24  32  40  48
```

Use only these values for padding, margin, and `SizedBox`.

## Sizing

```dart
const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16, vertical: 8);
const SizedBox(height: 12);
BorderRadius.circular(16);
```

- Always use `const` for fixed `EdgeInsets`, `SizedBox`, `BorderRadius`.
- Common radii: `4`, `8`, `12`, `16`, `20`.

## Text Styles — `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.*`

```dart
// Predefined styles
Text('Hello', style: {{TEXT_COMMON}});                        // 14, w400, {{TEXT_DEFAULT}}
Text('Required', style: {{TEXT_LABEL_REQUIRED}});           // 14, w400, {{ERROR}}, bold
Text('Hint', style: {{TEXT_HINT}});                          // 14, w600, {{TEXT_LIGHT_GREY}}
Text('Disabled', style: {{TEXT_DISABLE}});                    // 14, w400, {{TEXT_GREY}}

// Factory widget
{{TEXT_WIDGET}}(
  title: 'Title',
  fontSize: 16,
  fontWeight: FontWeight.w600,
  color: {{BRAND}},
  maxLines: 2,
  overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis,
  textAlign: TextAlign.center,
);

// Span builder
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.textSpanWidget(
  title: 'bold span',
  fontSize: 14,
  fontWeight: FontWeight.w600,
  color: {{TEXT_DEFAULT}},
);

// Per-weight style builders
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getRegularStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getMediumStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getSemiBoldStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getBoldStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getLightStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
```

## Card / Container Pattern

```dart
Container(
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: Colors.white,
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16),
    border: Border.all(color: {{DIVIDER}}),
  ),
  child: ...,
)
```

## Dialogs — Triggered from Provider

```dart
// WRONG — called directly from widget
showDialog(context: context, builder: (_) => AlertDialog(...));

// CORRECT — dispatched via eventStream
provider.{{M_SHOW_DIALOG}}(
  type: {{DIALOG_TYPE_ENUM}}.success,
  title: {{I18N_CLASS}}.notification,
  content: {{I18N_CLASS}}.downloadDataSuccess,
  onActionCallback: (action) {
    if (action == DialogActionType.confirm) { ... }
  },
);
```

