## Theme & Font

- **Font: `{{FONT}}`** (`FontConstants.fontFamily`).
- Default `Scaffold.backgroundColor`: `Colors.white`.
- `TextScaler.noScaling` not yet globally enforced (TODO: add to root app).

## Localization

- Package: `easy_localization`.
- Files: `{{I18N_FILE_PATTERN}}`.
- Access via `{{I18N_CLASS}}` class (`lib/core/constants/app_strings.dart`):

```dart
{{I18N_CLASS}}.notification                    // → "Thông báo"
{{I18N_CLASS}}.warningNotConnectInternet       // → "Không thể kết nối..."
{{I18N_CLASS}}.thangChiCo30ngay(5)          // → "Tháng 5 chỉ có 30 ngày" (namedArgs)
```

- Key format: `{{I18N_KEY_STYLE}}` — NO `{{NO_LOCALE_KEYS}}` / `{{NO_PREFIX}}` convention.
- When adding a new string: add to all 4 JSON files + a getter in `{{I18N_CLASS}}`.

## DO / DON'T

| DO                                               | DON'T                                             |
|--------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| `{{BRAND}}`                                    | `Color(0xFF0057E5)`                               |
| `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.common`                   | `TextStyle(fontSize: 14, color: ...)` inline      |
| `{{TEXT_WIDGET}}(title: {{I18N_GETTER}})` | `Text({{I18N_GETTER}}, style: TextStyle(...))`   |
| `{{I18N_GETTER}}`                              | `'Thông báo'`                                     |
| `{{SVG_HELPER}}('assets/images/ic_xxx.svg', width: 24)` | `SvgPicture.asset(...)` directly            |
| `provider.{{M_SHOW_DIALOG}}(type: {{DIALOG_TYPE_ENUM}}.error, ...)` | `showDialog(context: context, builder: ...)` |
| `provider.{{M_SHOW_TOAST}}(...)` | `FToast().showToast(...)` directly |

## Review Checklist

- [ ] No hex literals outside `ColorApp`.
- [ ] No inline `TextStyle(...)` → use `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.*`.
- [ ] All user-facing strings via `{{I18N_GETTER}}`.
- [ ] `EdgeInsets`/`SizedBox` are `const`.
- [ ] Padding/margin follow the spacing scale.
- [ ] SVG loaded via `{{SVG_HELPER}}()`.
- [ ] Dialog/Toast triggered from provider, not from widget.
